functions.name: register
functions.description: Registers a new custom element to the application registry.

parameters.name: customElementImporter
parameters.description: Function used to import the webcomponent contructor.

functions.name: unregister
functions.description: Unregisters an existing custom element from the application registry.

parameters.name: tagName
parameters.description: Custom element tag name to be removed.

tags.name: returns
tags.description: True if tagName was found and unregistration was successfull, false otherwise.

functions.name: get
functions.description: Gets the list of registered custom elements as a list of candidates.
